  "title": "Accounts Officer/ Accounts Assistant #79722",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Building & Construction Equipment</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Accounts Officer/ Accounts Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Aljunied</li><li>Working Hours: 5.25 days (Monday-Friday, 9.00am - 6.00pm; Saturday, 8.30am – 12.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + PB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Process outgoing payments, including cheque issuance, telegraphic transfers, and GIRO.</li><li>Manage Accounts Receivable (AR) and Accounts Payable (AP) operations.</li><li>Post monthly journal entries for AR/AP-related transactions.</li><li>Maintain a partial set of accounts, handle data entry and invoice processing.</li><li>Administer and record petty cash transactions.</li><li>Prepare and reconcile Statements of Accounts.</li><li>Support month-end close, GST filings, and annual audit activities.</li><li>Organize and maintain an orderly filing system and documentation.</li><li>Ensure accurate records and adherence to accounting procedures.</li><li>Able to commence immediately or with short notice.</li><li>Undertake other ad‑hoc tasks as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>GCE O‑Level or a Certificate in Accounting/Finance (or equivalent).</li><li>Relevant industry experience is preferred</li><li>Proficient with Microsoft Office and professional email communication.</li><li>1 year of relevant accounting experience.</li><li>MYOB experience is highly valued.</li><li>Able to work independently and collaborate effectively within a team.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79722 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
